      • validate

        public List<Message> validate(DataValue value)
        Validates that the specified DataValue is an instance of this data definition.

        Validates that supplied value is not null and it's type matches the type of this definition.

        In addition, validates that value's name matches this definition name and value's fields are valid for this definition fields.

        Overrides:
        validate in class DataDefinition
        Parameters:
        value - the DataValue to validate
        Returns:
        a list of messages describing validation problems; empty list indicates that validation was successful
